headline: Lam Research (LRCX) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of semiconductor equipment maker Lam Research (NASDAQ:LRCX) jumped 2.7% in the afternoon session after the broader semiconductor sector rallied as Dutch chipmaking equipment giant ASML Holding reported stronger-than-expected orders, boosting investor confidence.
